{"id":"6794","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【时间旅行】回到过去？","content":"<p>不可能。</p>\n<p>自然界有着许多能量，光能、电能、热能、化学能、动能、势能等等。</p>\n<p>一旦开启返回过去的时空门，这些能量会回到一分钟前，然后再次进入这个门，再次弄出一组相同的能量，当能量到达一定程度，没有人阻止，就会导致时空门损毁。</p>\n<p>所以，我们做不出时空门，它会在做成的一瞬间被销毁。</p>","board_id":"7","board_name":"灌水池塘","updated_at":1507206338,"created_at":1507197915,"n_views":76,"n_replies":7,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}